{{> layout/header}}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/user-login.css">
<main class="cc-login-main">
    <section class="cc-login-shell">
        <div class="cc-login-form">
            <h1>CatchCatch</h1>
            <p class="cc-login-form__desc">로그인하고<br>다양한 공연을 만나보세요</p>
            {{#errorMessage}}<p class="cc-badge" style="margin-bottom:16px">{{errorMessage}}</p>{{/errorMessage}}
            <form action="/login" method="post">
                {{#_csrf}}<input type="hidden" name="{{parameterName}}" value="{{token}}">{{/_csrf}}
                <div class="cc-input-wrap">
                    <span class="cc-input-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
                    </span>
                    <input class="cc-input" type="email" name="email" placeholder="이메일" autocomplete="email" value="ssar@naver.com">
                </div>
                <div class="cc-input-wrap">
                    <span class="cc-input-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="4" y="10" width="16" height="10" rx="2"/><path d="M8 10V7a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v3"/></svg>
                    </span>
                    <input class="cc-input" id="loginPassword" type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" autocomplete="current-password" value="ssar1234">
                    <button class="cc-input-eye" type="button" data-toggle-pw="loginPassword" aria-label="비밀번호 보기" aria-pressed="false">
                        <svg class="cc-eye-icon cc-eye-icon--show" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 12s3.5-6 10-6 10 6 10 6-3.5 6-10 6S2 12 2 12Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
                        <svg class="cc-eye-icon cc-eye-icon--hide" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m3 3 18 18"/><path d="M10.6 10.6a3 3 0 0 0 4.2 4.2"/><path d="M9.9 5.2A10.7 10.7 0 0 1 12 5c6.5 0 10 7 10 7a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.4 3.3"/><path d="M6.4 6.4C3.6 8.2 2 12 2 12s3.5 7 10 7c1.5 0 2.8-.3 4-.8"/></svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="cc-login-options">
                    <label class="cc-check"><input type="checkbox" name="rememberId"> 아이디 저장</label>
                </div>
                <button class="cc-btn cc-btn--primary cc-btn--full" type="submit">로그인</button>
            </form>
            <div class="cc-divider">또는</div>
            <div class="cc-social-row">
                <a class="cc-social cc-social--kakao" href="https://kauth.kakao.com/oauth/authorize?client_id={{kakaoClientId}}&redirect_uri=http://localhost:8080/kakao-redirect&response_type=code">카카오로 로그인</a>
                <a class="cc-social cc-social--naver" href="/oauth2/authorization/naver">네이버로 로그인</a>
                <a class="cc-social" href="https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/v2/auth?client_id={{googleClientId}}&redirect_uri=http://localhost:8080/google-redirect&response_type=code&scope=profile email">Google 로그인</a>
            </div>
            <div class="cc-login-links">
                <a href="/join">회원가입</a><span>|</span><a href="/find-id">아이디 찾기</a><span>|</span><a href="/find-password">비밀번호 찾기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="cc-login-promo" style="--promo-img: url('{{#promoImageUrl}}{{promoImageUrl}}{{/promoImageUrl}}{{^promoImageUrl}}/images/sample/banner-main.svg{{/promoImageUrl}}')">
            <div class="cc-login-promo__content">
                <div>
                    <p>함께하는 순간,<br>잊지 못할 감동</p>
                    <h2>2026 전국투어<br>콘서트 <em>티켓 오픈!</em></h2>
                    <p>지금 CatchCatch에서<br>예매하고 특별한 경험을 즐겨보세요.</p>
                </div>
                <a class="cc-btn cc-btn--primary" href="/concerts">공연 둘러보기 →</a>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </section>
</main>
<script src="/js/user/login.js"></script>
{{> layout/footer}}
